{
  "stem": "8370.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And in 1940, I was approached by one of my school colleagues to join an underground.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And as I had matric, I was incorporated into the, of course, clandestine officer's school.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Due to the fact that I spoke fluently German, I was put into intelligence.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I was instructed to catch contact with the German officers to receive information, to collect information, what's going on in the army, especially after the outbreak of the war with Russia.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You must understand, it was impossible, for example, to destroy all the trains going to the east front.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So it was, it have to be very selective.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So it was important to know what kind of goods are most important for the front.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And this, you could have only from the officers or from the people coming back from the east front.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I mixed a little bit among them from one to another, introduced by one and to the other one.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so I organized me, I would say, a net of informer among the officers coming back from east front.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "One gave my address or telephone number to another one and say, well, when you come to Warsaw, we've got a friend, Mr.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Wolff.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was a German family name.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they, they had been not aware I am Polish or I am German or what I am.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He take you home.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He give you a good food and a drink and this.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this way, I was working and collecting the information and afterwards, pass my information to the higher level to my, I would say, controller, how you call it, in, in this kind of job.",
      "word_count": 35
    }
  ],
